    "However, GPT-4V had a higher sensitivity probably due its predilection for malignancy.",
    "This makes a small case for GPT-4V as a possible screening tool, although more robust analysis is required to evaluate its role for this purpose.Our study is not without limitations.",
    "First, we evaluate GPT-4V with a zero-shot prompting strategy and did not comprehensively evaluate its sensitivity to various prompting techniques.",
